{"tid":1121374,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"Samsung 推遲 Galaxy Fold 發售！將強化螢幕保護！","createTime":"2019-04-23T09:28:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-25T00:10:47.000Z","uid":109383,"like":12,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"61e88e900e1290e18b7ab05ebf68ed1150227ac6","tid":1121374,"uid":109383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T09:28:04.000Z","msg":"今天《華爾街日報》指 Galaxy Fold 會最少推遲一個月才發佈，但 Samsung 同時發表聲明指正在調查 Galaxy Fold 評測者出現的螢幕損壞問題，會在未來數周再公佈一個新的開售日期。由於要全面評估試用者的意見及進行更多內部測試，因此 Samsung 決定會推遲 Galaxy Fold 的開售時間，他們計劃數周內會再宣佈推出日期。<br />\n<br />\n另外，Samsung 表示初步發現<span style=\"color: red;\">螢幕問題可能是與鉸鏈的頂部和底部暴露區域受衝擊有關。</span>他們會對螢幕作出一些加強保護措施，也會加強一些用戶指引，讓用戶注意螢幕保護層。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n三星又黎用家問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />個個測試者都跌過部機？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37a05bfaaf786a174ebc36c4f92987fadcad51db","tid":1121374,"uid":109383,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T10:53:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wDPJS0X.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwDPJS0X.png&h=28f850f3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7b08113803c2f555008745093ace3847581b8e9c","tid":1121374,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T12:17:01.000Z","msg":"強化到摺唔到咪冇事囉"},{"pid":"a4910f7b3aa46d2ec821e0e4d75a8a9f205138ae","tid":1121374,"uid":159448,"like":4,"dislike":7,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T12:37:41.000Z","msg":"唔係出左條片係咁開合既咩 <br />\n姐係條片造假啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d06bc60152562d71ff5f9dcd7e5e3533fb399dc","tid":1121374,"uid":1888,"like":4,"dislike":4,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2